---
title: Chili Chili Bang Bang Chicken with Scallion Rice & Roasted Green Beans
description: Another work day, another dinner daydream. You know what we mean. You’re sitting at your desk and 2pm rolls around. Suddenly, all you can think is, “Dinner...what the heck am I going to eat for dinner?!” Well, we’ve got you covered. Here’s the plan: crispy panko-crusted chicken, fluffy scallion-flecked rice, and tender roasted green beans. To finish things off, the chicken is drizzled with a life-affirming ponzu chili mayo. Talk about a dream come true!
